# Wisp

- Tauri 2 + React + TypeScript + Vite; UI via shadcn/ui + Tailwind
- Default shell: fish -l; fallback documented in README
- Tab state in Zustand; PTY logic stays in Rust (src-tauri/)
- Read design-system/wisp/MASTER.md before UI changes
- Follow ponytail: minimal diff, reuse shadcn components, no new deps without reason
